HEADWORD: Abietene
<hw>Ab"i*e*tene</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>abies</ets>, <ets>abietis</ets>, a fir tree.]</ety> <def>A volatile
oil distilled from the resin or balsam of the nut pine (<spn>Pinus
sabiniana</spn>) of California.</def>⟦br⟧
